{"tid":906903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫女友影相攞景太盡？ 西環男子跣腳墮海","createTime":"2018-11-18T11:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T13:47:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aabc7ee68ae87ec0bfbdb8a0eeb78f6d618de372","tid":906903,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542539185_2c6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542539185_2c6b.jpg&h=3c12004f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環發生墮海意外，下午5時許，現場為域多利亞公眾殮房對出海邊，據報37歲姓葉男子替35歲女友影相時，不慎失足墮海，其女友見狀慌忙報案。水警輪接報趕至，將葉男救起，他拒絕送院。警方經初步調查，相信事件沒有可疑，列有人意外受傷。"},{"pid":"829a5497c5b61a30fa73c5fdf4e21cc3c6bde277","tid":906903,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"點遠炒條女都係短腳架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40078343f9dcb91f3508019379f16c33b7de9003","tid":906903,"uid":43041,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"死左直接入域多利亞公眾殮房"},{"pid":"7c49cacb8d619cec6453353d811941518493bfbe","tid":906903,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6399a6fd8242df9f4426be4d2bf87db9d93d9640","tid":906903,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"拍緊141廣告？"},{"pid":"9f822b2645835ba751106f6dfe8d887d84768fc8","tid":906903,"uid":62506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c49cacb8d619cec6453353d811941518493bfbe","tid":906903,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"最憎膠黑絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee21889f202aebaf7401c4d170c22056fcd1ff9","tid":